io.spine.grpc

Class LoggingObserver<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.grpc.LoggingObserver<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver<V>

    @Internal
public final class LoggingObserver<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements io.grpc.stub.StreamObserver<V>
    The StreamObserver which adds records to the log as its methods called.

    The observer gets a reference to the parent class for which to create a logger.
